description	"Jango Fett [Mandalorian]

The greatest bounty hounter in the galaxy, boasting a jetpack, grappling hook, a wristblade, strong dual pistols, damage resistances, and a few offensive gadgets.

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Beskar Armblade (Cyan)
-- Saber Chain Limit: 2
-- Saber Damage (100)
-- Saber Defense (1)
- Wrist Flamethrower (Thrower)
-- x64 longer reload
-- 50% less DMG
- WESTAR-34 Blaster Pistols (3)
-- 10% faster RoF
-- 20% more DMG
-- 5% faster velocity
-- 15% more FP dmg
-- 10% faster reload

^8Attributes:
- 20% less KB taken
- 10% more KB given
- Beskar (3)
- Dexterity (3)
- Blast Armor
- Healing (1)
- Tracking Beacon

^3Abilities:
- Jetpack
- Rocket ^3[CS1]
- Poison & Tracking Darts (6) ^3[CS2*]
- Gun Kick ^3[CS3]
- Grap Hook (3) ^3[CS4 Melee*]"
